Here is my latest map
**Jb_carceris**

Bz2 version can be found [here](http://www.gamemaps.nl/versluis/cstrike/maps/jb_carceris_beta04.bsp.bz2 "Bz2 Link")

I've been working on this for the last couple of weeks, and I finaly managed to get a Beta running. There are still some tweaks that have to be done.

Note that this is a Beta, next version will be much better. (Will add **HDR** and **bigger lightmaps!**)

In this classic map there can be found:

- Soccer
- Disco
- Pool
 - Waterpolo
 - Diving
- LR
 - Gun Toss
 - Arena
 - Shot 4 Shot
- Yard one
 - Hot Potato
 - 4 in a row
 - Jumping contest
- Yard two

The map itself is fully optimized, and not heavy for any server at all.

For any suggestions or feedback, please reply!
